CustomField.description: Indicates whether a pickup/delivery can be made from either side of the street, or the same side as the location. Possible values as returned by AME are 'SAME', 'ANY' or 'UNKNOWN'.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Indicates whether a pickup/delivery can be made from either side of the street, or the same side as the location.
CustomField.label: Location Side Of Street Code
